title: Ep - 56 - TRISHELLE CANNATELLA OF REAL WORLD LAS VEGAS
description:
Trishelle Cannatella from the MTV reality television series The Real World: Las Vegas discusses getting cast for the show, how Leonardo DiCaprio was a huge fan of the show, why she hated doing The Challenge, and how she knew Nick and Vanessa from The Bachelor would never last. Amanda and Ali from Things We’re Too Lazy To Blog About podcast help me review Dallas Cowboy Cheerleaders: Making The Team. Will Gilbert, a single start-up consultant from New Jersey is forced to watch A Night With My Ex on Bravo.
